title: HELLO
body:
So just after getting paid, I’ve paid bills and have already been dropped down to .49 cents on my account. Don’t ya just love living paycheck to paycheck in today’s society :) So for a little while I’ll be doing shaded headshots for $15. If that’s too much I’ll also be doing quick headshot sketch for a ko-fi! This is simply till maybe my next pay where I can HOPEFULLY save a little more and not be squeezed dry from rent and bills. 

Commission Info

Ko-Fi

I don’t like to sound desperate but just for this little bit of time, if you can help spread this I’d appreciate it tons!
